
@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Home - BabrberShop</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --white: #fff;
            --redBorder: #f030010;
            --redMain: #fd3946;
            --blueButton: #0050f0;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-image: linear-gradient(to top, #000 0%, #09203f 100%);
            height:100vh;
        }
        nav {
            margin: 4% 7%;
            z-index: 6000;
            position: fixed;
            width: 85%;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            background: var(--white);
            border: solid 3px red;
            transition: 0.5s;
            text-align: center;
        }

        ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
        }
        .logo {
            margin: -0.5rem 3rem;
            width: 4em;
            transition: 0.5s;
        }
        a{
            width: 25rem;
            margin:1%;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        li{
            color: black;
            text-decoration: none;
            font: bold 12pt Segoe UI;
        }
        section{
            background: #fff;
            position: absolute;
            margin: 15% 15%;
            width: 45%;
            height: 45%;
            display: flex;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .col_one h1{
            position: absolute;
            margin: 5% 15%;
            font: bold 18pt Segoe UI;
            width: 25rem;
        }
        .col_one p {
            position: absolute;
            margin: 20% 15%;
            font: bold 12pt Segoe UI;
            width: 25rem;
        }
        .col_one a {
            position: absolute;
            margin: 35% 15%;
            font: bold 12pt Segoe UI;
            background: var(--blueButton);
            text-align: center;
            width: 15rem;
            border-radius:10px;
            padding-top:2%;
            padding-bottom:2%;
            color: var(--white);
        }
        .col_two img{
            width:23rem;
            margin-left: 110%;
            transform: rotate(25deg);
        }
        footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            color: var(--white);
            background: #fd3946;
            border-top-right-radius: 15px;
            border-top-left-radius: 15px;
            z-index: 1000;
        }
            footer p {
                font: bold 16pt Segoe UI;
                margin: 0.5em 5.2em;
            }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><img class="logo" src="~/fonts/logo_semFundo.png"></li>
            <a href="" title="Agendar"><li>AGENDAR</li></a>
            <a href="" title="Consultar"><li>CONSULTAR AGENDAMENTO</li></a>
            <a href="../Login/Login" title="Sair"><li>SAIR</li></a>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    <section>
        <div class="col_one">
            <h1>AGENDAR DATA E HORA</h1>
            <p>Venha para o BarberShop reserve uma<br/>data e um horário e venha para a melhor<br/>Barbearia da Região.</p>
            <a href="">AGENDAR</a>
        </div>
        <div class="col_two">
            <img src="~/fonts/foto_homeCli.png"/>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer>
        <p>Rua Atlanta - 15, Osasco-SP</p>
        <p class="text-copy" style="font-style: italic">&copy;BarberShop</p>
        <p>1133651651</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
